name: EU TEAM ltd
goal: EuTeam is an international network whose aim is to sustain public and/or private bodies, SMEs, NGOs and non profit organisations to get closer to the funds directly controlled by the European Commission or by the Agencies responding to it, for different projects and project ideas.
